job_name = "CHAR_TEN_FEET_OF_STEEL"
description = "Hu Sanniang, Ten Feet of Steel. In the legend the warrior woman who fought the brotherhood, lost her whole family to its war, and was bound into it anyway. Here her protection-detail family is wiped in a single night, and she is taken in by the very band that broke them. She fights like vengeance with nowhere to land, loyal and unforgiving at once."
